Package: nle.api
Type: Package
Title: Pure-R OpenTimelineIO Document Model
Version: 0.0.2.17
Date: 2026-06-06
Authors@R: c(
    person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "troy.h@cball.ai",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4248-604X")),
    person("cornball.ai", role = "cph"))
Description: A dependency-light OpenTimelineIO ("OTIO") document layer in
    pure R. Provides constructors for the OTIO object model (timelines,
    tracks, clips, gaps, media references, rational times and time
    ranges), functional builders that return new objects, and readers and
    writers for canonical '.otio' files through 'jsonlite'. The optional
    'rotio' package validates output against the real OpenTimelineIO C++
    library. No compiled code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: jsonlite
Suggests: tinytest, rotio
